<%- include('partials/header') %>
<style>
  .hero-app { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2ECC71, #27AE60); color: white; padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; }
  .hero-app h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero-app p { font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .hero-app .phone-icon { font-size: 6rem; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .app-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .app-btns a { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 14px 28px; background: white; color: #333; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; }
  .features-grid { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 20px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .feature-card { text-align: center; padding: 32px; background: white; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
  .feature-card i { font-size: 2.5rem; color: #2ECC71; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .feature-card h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; color: #1B4F72; }
  .feature-card p { color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .pricing { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px 48px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .price-card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
  .price-card.featured { border: 3px solid #F39C12; position: relative; }
  .price-card.featured::before { content: '추천'; position: absolute; top: -12px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: #F39C12; color: white; padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .price-card h3 { color: #1B4F72; }
  .price-card .amount { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #E74C3C; margin: 16px 0; }
  .price-card .amount span { font-size: 1rem; color: #888; }
  .price-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: left; }
  .price-card ul li { padding: 8px 0; color: #555; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
  .price-card ul li::before { content: '✓ '; color: #2ECC71; font-weight: 700; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .features-grid, .pricing { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

<div class="hero-app">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="phone-icon">📱</div>
    <h1>로또벅스88 앱</h1>
    <p>언제 어디서나, 스마트한 번호 분석을 손안에서</p>
    <div class="app-btns">
      <a href="#" onclick="showToast('앱스토어 등록 준비 중입니다.', 'warning'); return false;"><i class="fab fa-apple"></i> App Store</a>
      <a href="#" onclick="showToast('플레이스토어 등록 준비 중입니다.', 'warning'); return false;"><i class="fab fa-google-play"></i> Google Play</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="features-grid">
  <div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-bell"></i><h3>실시간 알림</h3><p>당첨번호 발표 즉시 알림으로 결과를 확인하세요</p></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i><h3>AI 번호 분석</h3><p>머신러닝 기반 고급 분석 알고리즘</p></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i><h3>상세 통계</h3><p>번호별 출현 빈도, 패턴, 구간 분석</p></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i><h3>QR 스캔</h3><p>복권 QR 코드로 간편 당첨 확인</p></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-users"></i><h3>커뮤니티</h3><p>회원들과 번호 공유 및 소통</p></div>
  <div class="feature-card"><i class="fas fa-video"></i><h3>라이브 방송</h3><p>로또벅스88 실시간 분석 방송 시청</p></div>
</div>

<h2 style="text-align:center; color:#1B4F72; margin:40px 0 24px;">요금제</h2>
<div class="pricing">
  <div class="price-card">
    <h3>무료</h3>
    <div class="amount">0원</div>
    <ul>
      <li>당첨번호 조회</li>
      <li>기본 통계 보기</li>
      <li>번호 1게임 생성</li>
      <li>커뮤니티 이용</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="price-card featured">
    <h3>프리미엄 월간</h3>
    <div class="amount">9,900원<span>/월</span></div>
    <ul>
      <li>무제한 번호 생성</li>
      <li>AI 고급 분석</li>
      <li>패턴 인식 엔진</li>
      <li>실시간 알림</li>
      <li>광고 제거</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="price-card">
    <h3>프리미엄 연간</h3>
    <div class="amount">89,000원<span>/년</span></div>
    <ul>
      <li>월간 프리미엄 모든 기능</li>
      <li>연 2회 특별 분석 리포트</li>
      <li>전문가 1:1 상담 쿠폰</li>
      <li>25% 할인 혜택</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
